Volcano Calbuco erupted on Wednesday forcing 1,500 people to flee their homes . 
  A pair of white lights were spotted floating perilously close to the volcano in southern Chile . 
  Hundreds of people have filmed the eruption and its deadly ash cloud . 
  Some have suggested the lights were either police helicopters or an alien aircraft . 
  Volcano Cal Buco has been dormant for 40 years . 
 